<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL3">
<l>vētanūṟ pirāyam nūṟu maṉicartām pukuva rēlum</l>
<l>pātiyu muṟaṅkip pōkum niṉṟavip patiṉai yāṇṭu</l>
<l>pētaipā lakaṉa tākum piṇipaci mūpput tuṉpa</l>
<l>mātalāṟ piṟavi vēṇṭē ṉaraṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if the humans were to reach the age of one hundred [referred to in] the Vedas,</l>
<l>Half [of it] will be spent sleeping;</l>
<l>the remaining fifty years [will be spent in] child[hood], boy[hood] and that [youth],</l>
<l>disease, hunger, old age, [and] afflictions.</l>
<l>Therefore I do not desire [re]births, O You from the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
